/*


𝙑𝙤𝙜𝙪𝙚


𝘢 𝘛𝘶𝘮𝘣𝘭𝘳 𝘥𝘢𝘴𝘩𝘣𝘰𝘢𝘳𝘥 𝘵𝘩𝘦𝘮𝘦


𝙢𝙖𝙙𝙚 𝙗𝙮 𝙬𝙝𝙞𝙢𝙨𝙮𝙩𝙝𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙨.𝙩𝙪𝙢𝙗𝙡𝙧.𝙘𝙤𝙢
*/



@-moz-document url-prefix("https://www.tumblr.com/dashboard"), url-prefix("https://www.tumblr.com/dashboard")
{

/* Header */
.l-header-container--refresh {
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px hsla(0, 0%, 100%, .13);
    background-color: #C3AA96;
}
.compose-button {
    fill: #CDB5A3;
}

/* Body */
a,
body {
    color: #C3AA96;
}
body {
    font-family: -webkit-pictograph;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-style: italic;
}
.identity {
    background-color: #CDB5A3;       
}
.l-container.l-container--two-column-dashboard .l-content, .l-container.l-container--two-column .l-content {
    background-color: #C3AA96;
}
.l-container.l-container--two-column-dashboard .left_column {
    background-color: #BDA18E;
    margin-top: 10px;
}
.l-container.l-container--two-column-dashboard .right_column, .l-container.l-container--two-column .right_column {
    background-color: #BDA18E;
}
.post_avatar {
    background-color: #BDA18E;
}

/* Sidebar */
.identity .right_column:after {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #BDA18E, rgba(0, 25, 53, 0));
}
.identity .controls_section.user_list li .follow_list_item_blog:before {
    background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 25, 53, 0), #C3AA96) !important;
    border-right: 5px solid #C3AA96 !important;
}
.identity .controls_section.user_list li .follow_list_item_blog:before:hover {
    background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 25, 53, 0), #C3AA96) !important;
    border-right: 5px solid #C3AA96 !important;
}
.identity .controls_section.user_list li .follow_list_item_blog:before {
    background-image: linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,25,53,0),#C3AA96) !important;
    border-right: 5px solid #C3AA96 !important;
}
.right_column{
    background-color: #BDA18E;
}
.identity .right_column {
    color: #fff;
margin-top: 10px;
}
.identity .right_column:after {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,#BDA18E,rgba(0,25,53,0));
}
.sidebar_link.explore_link {
    color: #fff;
}

/*Radar Fix*/
.radar .radar_footer .radar_avatar::before {
    background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 25, 53, 0), #C3AA96);
}
.radar .radar_footer .radar_avatar::before:hover {
    background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 25, 53, 0), #C3AA96);
}
}
